OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Comedian and actor Steve Coogan is to  
OL,6, play the disgraced late TV personality 
OL,7, Jimmy Savile in a new BBC One drama.   
OL,9,FThe Reckoning, a mini-series, will tell
OL,10,Fthe story of the presenter's rise and  
OL,11,Fthe sexual abuse scandal that emerged  
OL,12,Fafter his death.                       
OL,14,FThe BBC said the team behind the drama 
OL,15,Fhad worked closely with those impacted 
OL,16,Fby Savile to ensure their stories were 
OL,17,Ftold with "sensitivity and respect".   
OL,19,FCoogan said he had not taken the       
OL,20,Fdecision to play Savile "lightly".     
